# BhanksNFT Collection

## Overview
BhanksNFT is an ERC-721 collection on Base.
Each NFT has a unique token ID starting from 0.

## Details
- Name: BhanksNFT
- Symbol: BNFT
- Standard: ERC-721
- Network: Base
- Mint price: 0.001 ETH

## How to mint
1. Connect your Coinbase Wallet or MetaMask
2. Make sure you are on Base network
3. Click Mint NFT on the mint page
4. Confirm the transaction in your wallet
5. Wait for confirmation — under 5 seconds

## Revenue
All mint revenue goes to the contract owner
via the withdraw() function.

